1.1.0.name: wordpress/grooveshark
1.1.0.description:
Currently, our plugin is incompatible with the latest version of Wordpress. To get your Grooveshark Widget on your blog, we recommend using:

  • Embedly, a Wordpress plugin that allows you to embed content from many of your favorite sites, including Grooveshark. The free version of Embedly allows you to embed up to 10,000 URLs per month and has a friendly interface.
  • You may also use Gigya code to embed a Grooveshark widget into your blog. A quick tutorial on how to create and embed a Wordpress widget is located here: Grooveshark Help
